Mix together the yoghurt, garam masala, chilli powder, lime juice, coriander and red chilli.Marinate the chicken in the yoghurt mixture for 5 minutes.Preheat the barbecue to hot. Alternatively you can cook the chicken under a hot grill.Thread the chicken onto the kebab skewers and cook on the barbecue until the chicken is tender and cooked all the way through.Serve with salad and pitta bread.